# PropFlux Contract Enforcement

- Supported ingestion format is only PropFlux-style JSON arrays of listing objects.
- Required fields: `title`, `price`, `location`, `bedrooms`, `bathrooms`, `property_type`, `description`.
- Keep runtime schema and docs synchronized when fields change.
- Reject malformed input with explicit validation errors (index and field-level context).
- Add fixture coverage for valid payloads and each invalid class of payload.
